com.team1389.hardware.inputs.software

Class RangeIn<T extends Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1389.hardware.inputs.software.RangeIn<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type that the doubles in the stream represent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AngleIn, PercentIn

    public class RangeIn<T extends Value>
extends java.lang.Object
    an input stream of doubles with a range and stream operations to do math on the stream as values flow through
    Author:
    amind
